## Starting a Session

```bash
cd {{PROJECT_PATH}}
claude --agent orchestrator
```

Then provide direction. You can be specific or vague — the orchestrator handles both:

> [Your priorities for this session]

Or just:

> Go. Find what needs improving and improve it.

## Resuming After a Break

Same as above — start a fresh orchestrator session and say:

> Continue from where we left off.

The orchestrator reads CHANGELOG.md, IMPROVEMENTS.md, and recent reports to pick up context.

If you want to redirect:

> Continue from where we left off. Focus on {{specific area}} this session.

## Ending a Session

Say:

> Wrap up this session. Write a summary and update all tracking files.

This ensures CHANGELOG.md, IMPROVEMENTS.md, and the debrief are current for next time.

