## Session Patterns

### Quick fix (15-30 min)
```
Start → "Fix [specific issue]" → Test → Review → Commit → Exit
```

### Deep work (1-2 hours)
```
Start → "Run the improvement loop. Focus on [area]. Check in every 2 cycles."
→ Review check-ins → Redirect if needed → "Wrap up" → Exit
```

### Exploration (30-60 min)
```
Start → "I want ideas, not changes. Analyse [area] and tell me what's possible."
→ Read proposals → Decide what to pursue next time → Exit
```

### Scrutiny (30-60 min)
```
Start → "Have the scrutinizer tear apart our approach."
→ Read findings → Discuss → Exit
```

